''Germanic cognates:'' Old Saxon [[weg#Old Saxon|weg]] (Dutch [[weg#Dutch|weg]]), Old High German [[weg#Old High German|weg]] (German [[Weg]]), Old Norse [[vegr]] (Swedish [[väg]]), Gothic [[𐍅𐌹𐌲𐍃]].

''Indo-European cognates:'' Latin [[vehere]].

